    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.21 - v1 + 0.22)) / ((v0 + 0.58 + v2 + 0.72) * (v0 + 0.96 - tmp + 0.88)))
    v2 = 0.76
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.60) / v2))
    v2 = ((v1 / (v0 + 0.45 - v0 + 1.00)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.70) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.51)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v0 + 0.58) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.92)))
    data[tid] = v0
